description:
This is a 9 minute workout called '100 Pushups Workout | Do This Everyday' from the channel THENX.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
The workout has a The Disciplined Grind and The Progression Quest vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Follow along with Chris Heria as he completes this 100 Pushup Workout that you can do everyday for Insane Results. This workout will help you build discipline and improve your physique, strength, and performance.
